Azure Permissions by Input — Splunk Add-on for Microsoft Cloud Services
🔐 App Registration Prerequisites (All Inputs)
For all inputs that use an Azure App Account, you need a registered application in Microsoft Entra ID with the following credentials noted: Client ID, Key (Client Secret), and Tenant ID. ￼

